snippet.title: Saturated Outer Space | Gameplay trailer
snippet.description:
Saturated Outer Space is a turn-based strategy game with tactical gameplay.
Lead a squad and set a course towards the outer space! 🚀🌌

If you are encouraged by our game and would like to support us please like 👍 the video and subscribe ✅ to our YouTube channel!
